{!<tr><td style='height: 2em; background-color: #008000; color: white; text-align: center; border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;'>!}**[+ independence_parlament_pv +]%**{!</td><td style='background-color: #b1b0aeff; color: black; text-align: center'>!}**[+ nonaligned_parlament_pv +]%**{!</td><td style='background-color: #c30000; color: white; text-align: center; border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0;'>!}**[+ unionist_parlament_pv +]%**{!</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}
{!<div style="font-style: italic; margin-left: 3em">Popular vote</div>!}

{!<table style='border-spacing: 0px; margin-right: 1em; margin-left: 1em; width:95%; table-layout: fixed; margin-top:-0.75em;'>!}
{!<tr><td style='overflow:hidden; white-space: nowrap; width: !}[+ independence_parlament_spc +]{!%; height: 2em; background-color: #008000; color: white; text-align: center; border-radius: 3px 0 0 3px;'>!}**[+ independence_parlament_s+]** ([+ independence_parlament_spc +]%) {!</td><td style='overflow:hidden; white-space: nowrap; width: !}[+ nonaligned_parlament_spc +]{!%; background-color: #b1b0aeff; color: black; text-align: center'>!}**[+ nonaligned_parlament_s+]** ([+ nonaligned_parlament_spc +]%) {!</td><td style='overflow:hidden; white-space: nowrap; width: !}[+ unionist_parlament_spc +]{!%; background-color: #c30000; color: white; text-align: center; border-radius: 0 3px 3px 0;'>!}**[+ unionist_parlament_s+]** ([+ unionist_parlament_spc +]%) {!</td></tr>!}
{!</table>!}
{!<div style="font-style: italic; margin-left: 3em">Parlament control</div>!}

[? if ciu_parlament_s > 0 : Note: CiU has been unclear about their position on independence, so it is counted as unaligned. ?]

**Results by Constituency**

{!<div id="cat-polls-widget-wide" style="margin-top: -2em"></div>!}

**Government Formation**

[? if ciu_parlament_showviz: CiU will be able to form a <span style='color: var(--ciu); font-style: italic;'>minority government</span> with ERC's support. ?]

[? if jxsi_parlament_showviz: jxsi will need CUP's support to form a <span style='color: var(--jxsi); font-style: italic;'>Sovereignty government</span>. ?]

[? if jxcat_parlament_showviz: JxCat and ERC will form a <span style='color: var(--jxcat); font-style: italic;'>sovereignty</span> <span style='color: var(--erc); font-style: italic;'>government</span> with CUP's support. ?]
[? if not (ciu_parlament_showviz or jxsi_parlament_showviz or jxcat_parlament_showviz): How did we get here??? ?]

- @election_simulation: Reset simulation

@post_election_sim_congreso
set-bg: img/congreso.jpg
on-arrival: {!
var congreso_size = 0;
for (var constituency of Q.congreso_constituencies) {
    congreso_size += Q.congreso_seats[constituency];
}
Q.congreso_s_majority = Math.floor(congreso_size/2) + 1;

console.log("Total seats: " + congreso_size + ", majority: " + Q.congreso_s_majority);
!}
