[? if bcomu_local_barcelona_s = 11: Ada Colau will lead a bcomu <span style="color: var(--bcomu); font-style: italic;"> minority government</span> with the support of ERC, PSC, and CUP. ?]
[? if bcomu_local_barcelona_s = 10: Ada Colau will lead a bcomu-pscbcn <span style="color: var(--bcomu); font-style: italic;">coalition</span> <span style="color: var(--psc); font-style: italic;">government</span> with the support of csbcn. ?]

- @local_cat_results: Catalonia is not only Barcelona, though...

@local_cat_results
on-arrival: {!
    if (Q.bcomu_local_barcelona_s == 11 || Q.bcomu_local_barcelona_s == 10) {
        Q.local_barcelona_wp = "bcomu";
    }
!}

